es as a geological laboratory, part 1: Turbidity currents (1985) Naturwissenschaften, 72, pp. 315-321; Janensch, W., Beiträge zur Kenntnis der Karru-Schichten im Östlichen Deutsch-Afrika (1927) Palaeontographica Supplement, 7, pp. 107-142; Kaaya, C.Z., Depositional environment of Late Permian Karoo beds in the Ruhuhu Basin and Mikumi area of Tanzania (1992) Geologisches Institut Universität Köln Sonderveröffentlichungen, 83. , 126p. Cologne, Germany; Kreuser, T., Late Paleozoic glacial sediments and transition to coal-bearing Lower Permian in Tanzania (1987) Facies, 17, pp. 149-158; Kreuser, T., Permo-Trias im Ruhuhu-Becken (Tansania) und anderen Karoo-Becken von SE-Afrika (1990) Geologisches Institut Universität Köln Sonderveröffentlichungen, 75. , 122p. Cologne, Germany; Kreuser, T., Wopfner, H., Kaaya, C.Z., Markwort, S., Semkiwa, P.Z., Aslanidis, P., Depositional evolution of Permo-Triassic Karoo basins in Tanzania with reference to their economic potential (1990) Journal African Earth Sciences, 10, pp. 151-167; Markwort, S., Sedimentation und diagenese der triassischen Karoo-Schichten des Ruhuhu-Beckens, Tansania (1991) Geologisches Institut Universität Köln Sonderveröffentlichungen, 80. , 118p. Cologne, Germany; Martin, H., The Late Palaeozoic Gondwana glaciation (1981) Geologische Rundschau, 70, pp. 480-496; Mazurczak, B., Notes on the Ruhuhu Coalfields (Southern province, Tanganyika Territory) (1953) Colonial Geological Mineral Resources, 3, pp. 239-241; Mbede, E.I., Tectonic development of the Rukwa Rift Basin in SW Tanzania (1993) Berliner Geowissenschaftliche Abhandlungen Reihe A, 152. , 92p. Berlin; McKinlay, A.C.M., Geology of the Ketewaka-Mchuchuma Coalfield, Njombe District (1954) Geological Survey Tanganyika Bulletin, 21. , 46p. Dodoma, Tanganyika; McKinlay, A.C.M., The coalfields and the coal resources of Tanzania (1965) Geological Survey Tanzania Bulletin, 38. , 82p. Dodoma, Tanzania; Menning, M., A numerical time scale for the Permian and Triassic